Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 名不虚传
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是联邦军总司令部巨环基地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次进到内部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像乡巴佬进城 连我都不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第7战队部署在斯坦宇域078
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第42战队…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这座基地的司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特·明日野中将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了就好 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久未问候 明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战舰歌姬号 方才抵达巨环基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍后汇报详细情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号原本要前往地球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于情况特殊 计划改变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘即将大举进攻巨环基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情报部已经掌握相关信息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号须参加巨环基地的防卫战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大规模攻击 杰哈特也会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 从我面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是次世代机师特别训练测试
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是培养次世代机师的训练程序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是明日野司令开发的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过各种训练课目掌握机师特点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此为根据 培养机师的综合作战能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说可以测评机师的X-Rounder能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以接受测试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像主要是针对有5年以上驾驶经验的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没有太明确的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说可以接受测试？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 看那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 明日野司令的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新兵也想来接受特别测试？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先应该去哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然少尉也决定接受测试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有因为战绩上输给你这个下级士官…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 想发现自己的…可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合 说明测试详情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人把话说完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始 按要求进行个人测试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据测试结果分析机师特点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当场发表结果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝各位好运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越杰哈特 分秒必争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天也要超越爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？杰诺亚斯-2的维护记录？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 上次战斗时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉左腿反应迟缓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不麻烦的话 能让我看一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是杰诺亚斯-2不是我负责的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米 蕾米·卢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位中尉想看杰诺亚斯-2的维护记录
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维护记录吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我还有活要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的 上次战斗时感觉左腿响应迟缓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱动系统和新型数据传输系统的匹配性差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很早就注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经想好了解决方案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数据传输装置的校验方式采用的是SDK代码
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为接收装置安装对应补丁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来解码速度可以提高75% 加之…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加之？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加之 把这里的控制部件和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电力供应系统的接口…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没这样聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在船上几乎没机会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 这身制服是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 在参加特别测试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆也在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆为什么那么渴望变强？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了更好的胜任战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了更好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特是维甘人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次战斗 那台红色机体就是他驾驶的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 你们见过面了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他变了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你们见过面了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 你成绩怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 有你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-Rounder适应性… D
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去成不了X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆·明日野 亚瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近发生过什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为新兵成绩虽然不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但精神状态非常不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠着点 小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 他们给我看了你的测评结果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-Rounder适应性虽然是D
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是别灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要流着我们家族的血脉 没有什么做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 特别测试…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说了你的特训评价结果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厉害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是因为X-Rounder适应性D？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甭放在心上 没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说得这么轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受测试 就是为了更快的超越他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成不了X-Rounder的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂不是永远无法超越他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想退伍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时等你退伍申请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:13:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起打橡皮靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这儿有更适合发泄对象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫队长 这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也应该听说过这里的大名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦德纳工坊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦德纳工坊？就是这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫 你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接到联络我马上就赶来了 老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎啊 沃尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是那么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我要的东西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:13:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫洛蒂·麦德纳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的下任老板 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用怕那个老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来唬人 其实心肠软
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是个顺风耳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛蒂 那玩意儿准备好没？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等老爸的最终调试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做也可以 只怕您老不肯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 你还未够班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好严厉的师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想说呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没大没小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难伺候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听沃尔夫先生说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是菲利特·明日野司令的儿子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很辛苦吧 做名人的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老爸也是个名声在外的机械工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡事都被拿来和老爸比较
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 看你和老爸关系挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为打从心底里尊敬老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能因为从小在这里长大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉摆弄机动战士比什么都开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以选择了这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就撞见了不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的一堵墙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说 是自己的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一代就能建起这样的工坊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是每个人都行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近距离见识老爸干活的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真心佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想学到他的技术 然后超越他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:16:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在同一条路上 我也许无法胜过老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 做着做着发现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在有些方面 我有自己的特长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸是老爸 我是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子造的战斗模拟装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过 这里有更好的发泄对象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用的是废弃机动战士驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面塞满了最新型多尺度情景再现系统
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那些烂大街的模拟战装置不是一个概念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这方面不是我的特长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是小家伙在指手画脚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不快上去试试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然用的是杰诺亚斯的驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事先输入了高达AGE-2的机体数据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没空发呆 敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE-1使用了驱蝠战役时的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的 用的是之前的战斗数据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数据处理用了不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过能和你聊聊也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些数据是怎么搞到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从高达电脑里抽取的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是泄漏军事机密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克可高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有震动机能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别因为是模拟战就掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试吧 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是打赢老爸的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子要我对付这两台机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说泄气话 该怎么打怎么打
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特确实是个了不起的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 没必要样样模仿他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只管做自己擅长的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擅长的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有向任何人学过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就干掉了维甘的机动战士不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更自由地 更随心所欲的战斗就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更自由地 更随心所欲的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的方式去变强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正强大的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是这里强大！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮厉害的嘛 那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是自己的孩子 打分就留情了哈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为他能赢吗 沃尔夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多半不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至多坚持三分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 和老爸对战的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请再让我打一次 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 打到你满意为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有自己的特长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的方式去变强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的方式…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的方式变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨环基地攻略战即将准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你应该明白这次作战事关重大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只许成功不许失败
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要辜负我的期望 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心 伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了维甘所有人民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座巨环基地是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们联邦军保卫地球之要所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里若被攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球将轻易落入他们的魔爪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,策划攻势的维甘 必会调集大量兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也已尽可能抽调兵力 据守这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗必将空前激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我相信你们的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和作为地球联邦军的那份尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝各位好运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.13,0:22:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标 地球联邦军总司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨环基地
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------EDCN2------------------------------------
